snippet.title: Phoenix Point: Behemoth Edition - Launch Day Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10001032/

Face off against an evolving alien threat around the globe in Phoenix Point: Behemoth Edition, now available with 4 pieces of downloadable content, including the brand new Corrupted Horizons content. Redesigned from the ground-up with controller support in mind, and playable across PlayStation 4, PlayStation 4 Pro and the PlayStation 5 series of consoles.
